We are looking for a highly analytical and user-focused Product Owner for the Merchant Platform to join our team at MoMo. In this role, you will lead a team, research and analysis to understand user behavior, propose innovative payment services, and oversee product implementation to ensure continuous improvements. Your work will directly impact MoMo’s strategic direction, enhancing user experience and financial service offerings.
Being the owner of a merchant solution for offline merchants (f&b, retail,...), a product owner will be responsible for the product line’s successfulness. The product leader will manage the full circle of a product life (of payment models or payment services) from research, analysis, development, launching, operation process, and quality standards to ensure give both end users and merchants the best experience possible.
Research the market demands for innovative and convenient payments solutions and other services solutions for offline merchants. Develop new payment models, platforms and business services compatible with market demands and top-notch technologies/ devices;
Analyze the business requirements for each project. Set priorities for them based on the market/ business demands;
Provide user-oriented solutions based on the analysis via documentation;
Define the business logic approaches for them to be in cohesion with technical solutions which are provided by ITC;
Collaborate between cross functional teams during project development. Report in timely manner for project progress and risks management;
Plan and execute launch procedures for deploying new payment models or payment services;
Take good use of data statistics and feedbacks from all input channels (CEE, Merchant Care, Integration Force) to track end users and merchants behaviors, also to continuously evaluate the user journeys, product funnels and services quality, in order to make adjustments or enhancements in timely manner;
Maintain the quality standards of all merchant solution services on the merchant platform. Continuously improve the available merchant solutions service to better the user experiences.

- Chịu trách nhiệm hỗ trợ kỹ thuật trước và sau bán hàng cho các sản phẩm mạng, đảm bảo nhu cầu của khách hàng được giải đáp hiệu quả;
- Phụ trách lập kế hoạch mạng, thiết kế giải pháp mạng, lựa chọn thiết bị mạng, triển khai và lắp đặt;
- Chịu trách nhiệm bảo trì mạng và thiết bị hàng ngày, bao gồm quản lý thiết bị, xử lý sự cố, tối ưu hóa mạng, cấu hình, kiểm tra định kỳ, bảo trì thường xuyên và diễn tập khẩn cấp;
- Xây dựng quy trình vận hành và quy chế bảo trì liên quan đến quản lý mạng.

