Working in Product Growth Team, you will be responsible for driving platform user growth through the product development and for building the next leaders through your own hard work and leadership. You will work as a highly skilled Problem Solver to closely work with cross-functional teams including marketing, design, engineering and other product owners to identify the user problems and get them solved really really fast.
Define and prioritize growth initiatives based on user problems and business problems;
Collaborate with design and engineering teams to develop and launch needed features that drive user activation & retention;
Analyze and interpret data to identify areas for improvement, and to measure the impact of initiatives;
Talk to user, read users' complaints and feedbacks, conduct user research and usability testing to gain insights into user problem, user behavior and preferences;
Develop and maintain a deep understanding of the user problems & need, the business challenges, the competitive landscape and industry trends.
Build the next leaders throughout your dedication and strong leadership.

